- Initial public beta release
- EWMA baseline learning with 3-sample minimum
- Automatic protocol detection (Zigbee, Z-Wave, Matter, Hub Mesh, LAN)
- Health scoring: Excellent / Good / Fair / Poor / Offline
- Snooze per device with configurable duration and auto-expiry
- Mode restriction for notifications
- Pushover markup support
- Single `capability.*` device picker
- Collapsed settings sections with current value display
- NullPointerException fixes for fresh installs

